# Normalize every text file to LF in the repository and on checkout, matching
# .editorconfig (end_of_line = lf). Ends the mixed CRLF/LF blob drift that crept
# in from Windows autocrlf checkouts. `text=auto` lets git leave binaries alone.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit (also covered by the rule above): shell scripts and git hooks are LF.
*.sh text eol=lf
.githooks/* text eol=lf
